ull}, {"id": "2072670541018751161", "url": "https://x.com/InfinitusCap/status/2072670541018751161", "text": "Omg \nHOLD ON TO YOUR PANTS \nBecause he was dead wrong on March 9\n-\nCNBC's Jim Cramer has now completely flipped:  \"I am in the $50 to $45 camp!\"\nVideo from CNBC minutes ago\n-\n$CL_F #OOTT #CRUDEOIL #BRENT \n@OilHeadlineNews @JuliOnTwtr https://t.co/DjMHGvxU1I", "time": "13:15", "author": "InfinitusCap", "author_name": "Infinitus Capital", "followers": 5609, "views": 4531, "likes": 9, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072670951825608991", "url": "https://x.com/SpartaFreight/status/2072670951825608991", "text": "VLCC TD3c, LR2 TC5 &amp; MR TC14 conflict de-escalation trade scenarios: #oott https://t.co/nes3NkufyA", "time": "13:17", "author": "SpartaFreight", "author_name": "Michael Ryan", "followers": 1285, "views": 1375, "likes": 13, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072674829476446566", "url": "https://x.com/InfinitusCap/status/2072674829476446566", "text": "Jim Cramer (great contra indicator) is UBER bearish on 🛢️ #CRUDEOIL this morning \n-\nON MONDAY MARCH 9, HE WAS UBER BULLISH, CALLING FOR $150-$200, And was dead wrong.  Went straight down from that day.\n-\n$CL_F $67.60s right now \n-\n#OOTT\n@Futures06\n@trenderer798 https://t.co/Bn7ogo9DEa", "time": "13:32", "author": "InfinitusCap", "author_name": "Infinitus Capital", "followers": 5609, "views": 5322, "likes": 8, "replies": 3, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072707934757236808", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2072707934757236808", "text": "#Kuwait's crude oil production rose to 1.65 million barrels per day in June, a source familiar with the matter told Reuters on Thursday, sharply higher than May's average of 578,000 bpd. #oott https://t.co/kqjIJsPFct", "time": "15:44", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3672, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072716709383819412", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2072716709383819412", "text": "WTI &gt; $68, Brent &gt; $71.  \n\nThere is a 3-day weekend approaching with lots of fireworks expected. \n\n#OOTT", "time": "16:19", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 3021, "likes": 40, "replies": 2, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072717184384536736", "url": "https://x.com/InfinitusCap/status/2072717184384536736", "text": "#Crudeoil about to go green\n\nJim Cramer was UBER UBER bearish this morning on CNBC, calling for $45-$50 next\n\n$CL_F live quote:  $68.14\n\nWTI was $67.70s during his morning rant \n\n#OOTT #CL_F \n-\n@Energy_Tidbits @EnergyPhilFlynn @Ole_S_Hansen https://t.co/H90N5F4m4j", "time": "16:21", "author": "InfinitusCap", "author_name": "Infinitus Capital", "followers": 5609, "views": 1490, "likes": 3, "replies": 2, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072727091150201303", "url": "https://x.com/Rigzone/status/2072727091150201303", "text": "Russia's gasoline-supply crunch is starting to ripple into Central Asia.\n\nhttps://t.co/HUbcGWk6af\n\n#OOTT #oilgas #Russia #gasoline", "time": "17:00", "author": "Rigzone", "author_name": "Rigzone", "followers": 108893, "views": 865, "likes": 0, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072727365508038777", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2072727365508038777", "text": "US oil rigs +5 to 445\nBaker Hughes\n#oott", "time": "17:01", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 35632, "likes": 20, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072727994469159140", "url": "https://x.com/NoamRaydan/status/2072727994469159140", "text": "Additional VLCCs signaling for Basrah, Iraq: Peru Prosperity IMO 9418066, Suriname Prosperity IMO 9376749, and Dominica Prosperity IMO 9395496. So at least 7 VLCCs linked to Sinokor so far are expected to load in Basrah, based on AIS data. \n#Shipping #OOTT #Iraq https://t.co/ONYwvtB4gn", "time": "17:03", "author": "NoamRaydan", "author_name": "Noam Raydan", "followers": 7546, "views": 47850, "likes": 27, "replies": 1, "retweets": 12, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072741570583953683", "url": "https://x.com/Bacharelhalabi/status/2072741570583953683", "text": "More broadly, the narrative that the market is already awash with crude looks increasingly difficult to reconcile with relatively tight commercial inventories and continued draws from storage. Supply is recovering, but “oversupplied” still looks like a stretch. #oott", "time": "17:57", "author": "Bacharelhalabi", "author_name": "Bachar EL-Halabi | بشار الحلبي", "followers": 10292, "views": 5432, "likes": 22, "replies": 2, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072747058369376292", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2072747058369376292", "text": "Saudi crude and product exports were around 5.8mbpd in recent days rather than 6.3mbpd reported by some media outlets. The higher figure includes volumes from previously stranded cargos based on sources with knowledge about Saudi oil exports\n#oott", "time": "18:19", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5517, "likes": 27, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072757494678753684", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2072757494678753684", "text": "Saudi crude and products exports averaged around 5.8 mb/d, rather than the 6.3 mb/d reported by some, according to sources familiar with the matter. The higher figure includes volumes from previously stranded cargoes. #OOTT #SaudiArabia", "time": "19:01", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 43228, "likes": 128, "replies": 2, "retweets": 27, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072757684928176270", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2072757684928176270", "text": "The narrative of having a “glut” in the market is VERY misleading #OOTT", "time": "19:01", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 7451, "likes": 82, "replies": 3, "retweets": 11, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2072758583834669552", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2072758583834669552", "text": "Hormuz flows are FAR from being normal #OOTT", "time": "19:05", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 5429, "likes": 59, "replies": 10, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 31, "views": 140244, "likes": 221}, {"username": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "tweets": 6, "views": 14227, "likes": 99}, {"username": "InfinitusCap", "name": "Infinitus Capital", "followers": 5609, "tweets": 5, "views": 12577, "likes": 28}, {"username": "Rigzone", "name": "Rigzone", "followers": 108893, "tweets": 4, "views": 3247, "likes": 3}, {"username": "garquake", "name": "Burnsco", "followers": 32104, "tweets": 3, "views": 12392, "likes": 48}, {"username": "DB_WTI", "name": "WTI Trading Group- 🇺🇸 US Crude Oil Trader🛢️🌎", "followers": 12439, "tweets": 3, "views": 3628, "likes": 3}, {"username": "Amena__Bakr", "name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "tweets": 3, "views": 56108, "likes": 269}, {"username": "PetroleumEcon", "name": "Petroleum Economist", "followers": 67133, "tweets": 2, "views": 1656, "likes": 7}, {"username": "FluxOfficials", "name": "The Officials", "followers": 1859, "tweets": 2, "views": 1162, "likes": 7}, {"username": "csidetrader", "name": "Seas